         Your profile is currently being verified, and you shall be informed after verification is complete.<br><br>
         Kindly verify your email ID by clicking on the link below:<br>
         <a style="color: #0077b5;text-decoration:none;"href="${link}" target="_blank" >${link}</a><br><br>
         For any feedback regarding our services or the Healthcoco+ app, please feel free to contact us at <a style="color: #0077b5;text-decoration:none;"href="" target="_blank" >${contactUsEmail}</a>

          <br><br>Stay Healthy and Happy,<br>Team Healthcoco.
         </p>
        </div>
      </div>

